WEBVTT

00:00:00.853 --> 00:00:02.571
What do you think would happen

00:00:03.248 --> 00:00:06.153
if you invited an individual
who had been living on the street

00:00:06.177 --> 00:00:07.723
for many years,

00:00:07.747 --> 00:00:09.464
had mental health issues

00:00:10.457 --> 00:00:12.144
and was an alcoholic

00:00:12.168 --> 00:00:14.253
to move directly from the street

00:00:14.277 --> 00:00:15.670
into housing?

00:00:16.233 --> 00:00:19.150
We had heard this was being done
in New York City,

00:00:19.174 --> 00:00:21.175
and it was called the Housing First model.

00:00:21.199 --> 00:00:23.477
We wondered if it would work in Utah.

00:00:24.038 --> 00:00:27.703
So to make that determination,
we decided to create a pilot,

00:00:27.727 --> 00:00:32.978
and Keta was one of the 17
chronically homeless individuals